OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777581027
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FReferrals to the Encounter programme
OL,8,Fare now at an all-time high, with many
OL,9,Fparents like Sarah facing similar
OL,10,Fabuse and in urgent need of help.
OL,12,FAnother mother, Leanne, now works for
OL,13,Fthe charity Oasis which runs the
OL,14,FEncounter programme.
OL,16,FOasis is commissioned by Greater
OL,17,FManchester Violence Reduction Unit to
OL,18,Fsupport parents and carers in Greater
OL,19,FManchester who have concerns about
OL,20,Ftheir children or are worried they may
OL,21,Fbe at risk of violence
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777581027
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FLeanne said her ten-year-old
OL,8,Fdaughter's abuse became so bad she
OL,9,Fregularly had to call the police.
OL,11,FShe said: "I felt like that was the
OL,12,Fonly help I could get at that time.
OL,13,FIt's horrible to say that you're
OL,14,Fterrified of a child."
OL,16,FLeanne described how her daughter took
OL,17,Fcontrol of the house.
OL,26,@sD@KOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777581027
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe said "She controlled everything. I
OL,8,Fwasn't allowed to speak on the phone
OL,9,Fwith anybody. I lived in my bedroom
OL,10,Ffor a whole year. She'd pull my hair.
OL,11,FShe'd punch me."
OL,13,FLeanne says the charity gave her
OL,14,Ffamily hope again, but two years on
OL,15,Fher daughter is still waiting for an
OL,16,Fautism and ADHD assessment.
OL,18,FShe believes more needs to be done by
OL,19,Forganisations and authorities to
OL,20,Fsupport neurodivergent children and
OL,21,Ftheir families.
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777581027
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe said: "Schools need more
OL,8,Funderstanding. More education on
OL,9,Fneurodiversity. I get that they have
OL,10,F(Special Educational Needs
OL,11,FCoordinators (SENCOs)) but there's
OL,12,Fonly so much one SENCO can do in a
OL,13,Fschool with 50 students that are
OL,14,Fneurodivergent."
OL,16,FNicola Hill, team leader for Parent
OL,17,Fand Carer Support at Oasis, says early
OL,18,Fintervention is key to better long-
OL,19,Fterm outcomes and can reduce pressure
OL,20,Fon emergency services.
OL,26,@rD@ApmsD@Vpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
