FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777581027
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FShe said: "You have to work with the
OL,8,Findividual and some people might think
OL,9,Fthat's like labour intensive or we
OL,10,Fcan't spend that much time but our
OL,11,Ffamilies are ringing the police.
OL,13,F"They're ringing our services and
OL,14,Fputting in a great demand on emergency
OL,15,Fservices so we would eliminate that if
OL,16,Fwe are able to give these families the
OL,17,Fcorrect family support."
OL,26,@oD@KOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
