FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777581027
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,FAs referrals to Encounter reach record
OL,8,Flevels, both mothers hope their
OL,9,Fstories will highlight the urgent need
OL,10,Ffor better early intervention and
OL,11,Fsupport for families in crisis.
OL,13,FThe Home Office said: "Everyone should
OL,14,Ffeel safe in their own home and free
OL,15,Ffrom abuse. That is why we are
OL,16,Fimproving the response to child to
OL,17,Fparent or caregiver abuse - with
OL,18,Fprevention and early intervention at
OL,19,Fthe heart of our approach.
OL,26,@uD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777581027
OL,3,C'I locked myself in my room': Parents
OL,4,Cin fear of their children with no
OL,5,Csupport
OL,7,F"We have introduced a range of
OL,8,Fmeasures to better support children
OL,9,Fand their families including
OL,10,Fdeveloping a statutory definition of
OL,11,Fchild to parent abuse along with
OL,12,Fupdated guidance, as well as
OL,13,Fintroducing a new helpline for young
OL,14,Fpeople concerned about their own
OL,15,Fbehaviour."
OL,17,FFor more information about the
OL,18,FEncounter programme, you can find out
OL,19,Fmore on their website.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
